Goodwood Festival of Speed 2025 - Structure hire

Includes
•	20 x 35 x 7 double deck temporary structure system - as per visuals from last year
•	Heavy duty cassette floor (5kN/m2) throughout with integral base plates
•	Aluminium frame construction with thermo PVC roof covers
•	1no. internal and 1no. external staircase - (TBC)
•	Glass, doors and solid panel facade as per 2024 design
•	Vertical spoke design balustrade
•	Preparation of all necessary health & safety documentation in accordance with Construction CDM Regulations and Temporary Demountable Structure (TDS) guidance
•	Structure project manager to oversee project and attend production meetings etc.
•	Structure foreman and competent crew for install/dismantle including accommodation, subsistence and travel, as required
•	Fully equipped tool van on site for duration of install/dismantle
•	All plant required for the install/dismantle (Forklifts, 360 telehandler, cranage, powered access, glass lifter)
•	Project specific engineering, drawings and structural Calculations
•	Ground levelling system based on site levels being same as 2023 Lotus plot
•	Haulage of all equipment to/from site
•	Lifting and powered access equipment for install/dismantle
•	Project specific engineering, drawings and structural calculations

Not Included
• Power generation/distribution
• HVAC (heating, ventilation and air conditioning) 
• Internal/external lighting
• Internal/external tension fabric graphics
• Internal/external floor finishes (including any sacrificial sub-floor)
• Access steps/ramps
• Powder coated upright covers
